      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’ll enlighten your darkened heart with light,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Forgive your sins and rescue you with might;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He will cleanse you from all stains with His blood,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And give to you the life of God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So you need Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In your living there is a lack you sense,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And thru the years it grows the more intense;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Only Jesus this need can satisfy;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All vanity He will defy,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So you need Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You need Jesus! You need Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Men and women all need Him!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To escape from vanity,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To obtain reality,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To make life significant,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, you need Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All this world now is rife with toil and pain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In troubled times there’s nothing to sustain;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All is empty, on what can you rely?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All things reveal and testify"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That you need Jesus!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
